description:
Kingdom Hearts is a series of third-person action RPG's developed by Square Enix. With the Kingdom Hearts Series making their way to Steam recently, take a look at this overview guide going over the order players should experience these games ordered by Square Enix. The Kingdom Hearts Series is available now on PC (Steam).

#KingdomHearts #IGN #Gaming
title: Kingdom Hearts - Official 'What Order Should You Play Kingdom Hearts' Overview Trailer

description:

description: Of all the unlockables in The First Descendant, none are bigger game changers than the playable characters, each with their own unique abilities and build crafting potential. But if you’d rather not shell out real-world money to take one for a spin, here’s a guide on how to unlock First Descendant characters for free.
title: The First Descendant: How to Unlock New Characters for Free
